	measure 'Engineering Design to Debug Ratio' = ```
			
			VAR DesignHours = [Engineering Design Hours]
			
			VAR DebugHours = [Engineering Debug Hours]
			
			VAR Result = 
			    IF(
			        DebugHours < 200 || ISBLANK(DebugHours),
			        BLANK(),
			        DIVIDE(DesignHours, DebugHours)
			    )
			
			
			RETURN Result
			```
		formatString: 0.00
		lineageTag: 8ae7c1b1-84b6-450d-ab46-8e58e3fc9f93

